fr.inrialpes.exmo.align.impl.renderer

Class RelationTransformer

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.inrialpes.exmo.align.impl.renderer.RelationTransformer

  • public class RelationTransformer
extends java.lang.Object
    This class categorises relations of the API implementation with respect to the category of their use by renderers. It is made for being used _statically_ by renderers to decise how to render a cell. In principle, this is the only thing that has to be modified when using different Relation implementations.
